snippet.title: Rain on Your Parade - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Travel the world as a cute cardboard cloud and ruin everybody's day! Unlock new methods of mischief in over 50 levels, each with unique setting and objectives. This is the ultimate schadenfreude simulator.

Coming to PC, Nintendo Switch and Xbox One

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1213230/Rain_on_Your_Parade/

More Info: http://unboundcreations.com/games/rain-on-your-parade/

-------------
Trailer Editor - Dino Katherine (trailergoblin.com)
